  border-radius: 5px;
  cursor: pointer;
}function generateSignal() {
  const signals = [
    "📈 Buy XAU/USD (Gold) - RSI < 30, EMA Crossover, FII Positive",
    "📉 Sell XAU/USD - RSI > 70, EMA Reversal, DII Pressure",
    "⚠️ Wait - No Confirmed Signal"
  ];

  const signal = signals[Math.floor(Math.random() * signals.length)];
  document.getElementById("signal-output").innerText = signal;
}# Fuzion - AI Trading Signals Web App

This is a simple AI-based Forex (Gold XAU/USD) Signal Generator Web App.

### Features:
- ✅ Smart Money Strategy Based Signal
- 📊 RSI + EMA Crossover Logic
- 🇮🇳 FII/DII Confirmation
- 🎯 Auto TP/SL Logic Simulated

### How to Use:
1. Open `index.html` in any browser.
2. Click "Generate Signal".
3. Follow the BUY/SELL suggestion for Intraday Trading.

Made for educational purposes.
